               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat Prayers, Image of John the Baptist, መልክአ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ፡, Hymn to the Archangel Fanuel, “Greeting to you, Who Sends Away Demons,” ሰላም: ለከ: ሰዳዴ: ሰይጣናት: ፋኑኤል:</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="1v" facs="001">Fols 1r–1v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer of the Archangel Mika’el</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>which is written on his left and right wings</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="2r" to="11v" facs="002">Fols 2r–11v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2999RepCh279">Hymn to John the
                                                  Baptist</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="12r" to="12v" facs="012">Fols 12r–12v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for multiplying the grain in threshing</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="13r" to="14v" facs="013">Fols 13r–14v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2765RepCh49">Malkǝʾ-hymn (Salām)
                                                  to Phanuel</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="15r" to="20v" facs="015">Fols 15r–20v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1113Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa
                                                  bǝrhān</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="21r" to="22r" facs="021">Fols 21r–22r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for binding demons, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት: በእንተ: ማዕሠረ: አጋንንት:</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from="22r" to="22v" facs="022">Fols 22r–22v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Resurrection">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿǝmāda mǝśṭir, Mystery ofthe
                                                  Resurrection (ምሥጢረ፡ ትንሣኤ፡)</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="23r" to="23v" facs="023">Fols 23r–23v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Charm, Ṣälot Bä’ǝntä Śǝray, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሥራይ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>written in a different hand on sheets of a different size than those in the rest of the codex</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9"><locus from="23v" to="26r" facs="024">Fols 23v–26r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against charm, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10"><locus from="26r" to="28v" facs="026">Fols 26r–28v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against demons, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መፍርህ: ወመደንግፅ:</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
